{"tid":1436213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"gazette係 香港憲報!!! 咪俾人帶風向!! 要林鄭親口講撤回!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-09T08:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:10:00.000Z","uid":284295,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1ddd84df169cb8e22c99821d0b8f9379dd60e1","tid":1436213,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"憲報刊登於 2019 年 07 月 12 日 星期五 第 23 卷第 28 期 - 第3號法律副刊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20192332/cs320192332999.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20192332%2Fcs320192332999.pdf&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=5fb37cc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20192332/cs320192332999.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\ngazette係 香港憲報<br />\n逢星期五出版<br />\n《香港憲報》分為7部分：<br />\n<br />\n「政府公告」，內容是政府官方委任令、法定公告及政府招標等； [1]<br />\n「第1號法律副刊」，香港條例的新增或修訂公告，例如《2006年為僱員權益作核證(中醫藥)(雜項修訂)條例》； [2]<br />\n「第2號法律副刊」，法律規例，例如法定巴士路線； [3]<br />\n「第3號法律副刊」，條例草案，例如《非應邀電子訊息條例草案》； [4]<br />\n「第4號特別副刊」，註冊/牌照人士名單，例如地產代理牌照名單 [5]、註冊醫生 [6] 及幼兒中心等名單 [7] ；<br />\n「第5號特別副刊」，草案擬本、行政命令[8]、國務院令及國際協定等； [9] 及<br />\n「第6號副刊」，公共啟事，例如有限公司清盤會議通知、業務轉讓、拆夥及商標註冊申請等。 [10]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家仲記唔記得真係撤回既23條</span></span><br />\n憲報刊登於 2003 年 02 月 14 日 星期五 第 7 卷第 7 期<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20030707/cs3200307077.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20030707%2Fcs3200307077.pdf&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=e3977efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20030707/cs3200307077.pdf</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">THE LINK IS DEAD!</span><br />\n<br />\n2003 年 9 月 5 日，董建華被迫宣佈撤回《國家安全（立法條文）條例草案》<br />\n憲報刊登於 2003 年 12 月 12 日 星期五 第 7 卷第 50 期<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20030750/cs320030750999.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20030750%2Fcs320030750999.pdf&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=4e1aa577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20030750/cs320030750999.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n到十二月都睇到有嫁!!!!!!<br />\n即係呢個係一份記錄!!!!!!"},{"pid":"beca8c1d6afc61fb3c20e45303a0419e4d13a297","tid":1436213,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"0ff437da3b62ccbd14d0c59ea4a999aa0f657f75","tid":1436213,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8d8371919d06de9d2fa378d5dc418515811c7da8","tid":1436213,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"1a7ab44ebf7cdf5dd8affed09e70367ca658768f","tid":1436213,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02815a1da7a8d42674e0cd0e84878bad79af9383","tid":1436213,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"重要"},{"pid":"79907162f73966000249550f8cdd03084ade1408","tid":1436213,"uid":284295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"341ade06066d2e121187901d4908cbee72d7f612","tid":1436213,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9eabb2554b96879e953f6339267088f7d654ea54","tid":1436213,"uid":284295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b93847c52ca3dc5b4c6920ed08ca589eb38b23a4","tid":1436213,"uid":179918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n很重要"},{"pid":"7bfcddc652ac60a024e